---
title: Italian Cheesy Chicken Burger with Caramelised Onion & Fries
description: Bring a little Italian flair to burger night by using classic flavours such as caramelised onion, Italian herbs, Parmesan and dill-parsley mayo to turn a tender chicken fillet into a filling supreme burger.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/italian-cheesy-chicken-burger-beetroot-relish-49c47722.jpg
